QuestData.Title: Battle At The Iron Front
QuestData.Description: General, our troops are currently engaged in a conjoined assault at the Iron Front. The fight has been raging for some time now, and casualties are high.$b$bReport to the Iron Front and lend your strength to the war effort. I have no doubt that your presence on the battlefield will inspire the soldiers to victory!
QuestData.LogDescription: Aid the Alliance and Horde assault at The Iron Front in Tanaan Jungle.

Objectives.Objective: Aid In The Battle At The Iron Front
